  "text": "Intraurethral replacement plastic [CITATION_1] 21 ANTA, described in 2012, is one of the most complex of substitute urethroplasty methods. This technique is performed with strictures of the proximal part of the bulbar urethra. In the BMP of the urethra this method is not applicable.",
